00:01:37.159 --> 00:01:39.999
And you take that to
the three-halves power.

00:01:39.999 --> 00:01:41.339
So, this was the formula

00:01:41.339 --> 00:01:44.099
and I'm not a huge fan
of memorizing formulas

00:01:44.099 --> 00:01:45.639
